I remeber playing aD&D and being a summoner..it was cool to summone different stuff..not just eliementals, monsters, or weapons...but other things like giant swarms of flies or a horse or a ball of light that would float at my sholder. Perhaps our class could get more imaginative about our summons. different thing would add coler to the class...maybe even some things that would be wanted by others, like....a shield that has a fire shield on it and would burn enything trying to beat on the user..and that dmg shield and AC would get higher as the mages level would increase. Or perhaps a 'bandage of marr' that would heal 50% more hp with the bind wound skill...this is just my thoughts..i read things on boards and watch others play (yadda yadda yadda) and i think to my self on what i would do to make the class more fun. oh well...thats my two coppers worth.
</FONT>
